org.eclipse.incquery.runtime.api

Interface IModelConnector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EIQEditorModelConnector, EMFModelConnector, GMFModelConnector, GraphitiModelConnector

    public interface IModelConnector
    This interface provides all api calls for an instance model registered in the Query Explorer. Implementations of this interface should contain the editor specific handling of loadModel, unloadModel, getNotifier and showLocation methods.
